Package io.cui.test.valueobjects.contract

Provides implementations for the contracts defined at io.cui.test.valueobjects.api.contracts and ObjectTestContracts
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeanPropertyContractImpl<T>
    Tests all given properties according to the given List of PropertyMetadata
    BuilderContractImpl<T>
    Defines basic tests for builder.
    ContractRegistry
    Helper class handling the registration of TestContracts
    CopyConstructorContractImpl<T>
    TestContract for dealing Constructor and factories, VerifyConstructor and VerifyFactoryMethod respectively
    EqualsAndHashcodeContractImpl
    Helper class providing base functionality for test for the Object.equals(Object) and Object.hashCode() variants of classes.
    MapperContractImpl<S,​T>
    Defines tests for Mapper
    ObjectCreatorContractImpl<T>
    TestContract for dealing Constructor and factories, VerifyConstructor and VerifyFactoryMethod respectively
    ReflectionUtil
    Simple Helper for reflection-api.
    SerializableContractImpl
    Tests whether the object in hand implements Serializable and than serializes / deserializes the object, and compares the newly created object with the original by using Object.equals(Object)
    ToStringContractImpl
    Checks whether the object in hand implements Object.toString() and calls it will fully populated object.
